<!-- Maroon Health Summaries -->
<h2>Mission Statement</h2>
<p>Maroon Health Free Clinic is a Texas A&M medical student-run free clinic in Houston operating through a partnership with Open Gate Homeless Ministries. Every other Sunday, we provide medical care to individuals experiencing homelessness in the Montrose neighborhood.</p>

<!-- Services We Offer -->
<h2>Services We Offer</h2>
<p>We are a walk-ins only clinic and offer check-ups, wellness visits, sick visits, blood pressure checks, and wound care.</p>

